<form action="/rnode/<%= host %>/<%= port %>/vnc.html" target="_blank">
  <input type="hidden" name="autoconnect" value="true">
  <input type="hidden" name="password" value="<%= password %>">
  <input type="hidden" name="port" value="<%= port %>">
  <input type="hidden" name="host" value="<%= ondemand_host %>/rnode/<%= host %>/<%= port %> ">
  <input type="hidden" name="resize" value="remote">
  <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">
    <i class="fa faeye"></i> Connect to Desktop
  </button>
  <hr>
  <p>You can use the button above to reconnect if you closed the remote desktop window with time remaining. The session will end if time runs out or the job is cancelled.</p>
  <p>To manually end the session, double-click <strong>End Session</strong> on the desktop. You will also need to manually close the browser window.</p>
</form>
